             were indicted for <rs id="t18320906-274-off1540" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320906-274-off1540" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320906-274-off1540" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320906-274-cd1541" type="crimeDate">2nd of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-274-off1540 t18320906-274-cd1541"></join>, 1 waistcoat, value 10s.; 5 handkerchiefs, value 10s.; 2 shirts, value 2l., and 4 sovereigns, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-274-victim2251" type="victimName">
